'From Squeak3.10beta of 22 July 2007 [latest update: #7137] on 20 November 2007 at 12:41:02 am'!"Change Set:		CharacterSet-copy-Patch-M6777-niceDate:			20 November 2007Author:			niceCharacterSet copy is shallow: changing a copy changes the original.This is a patch."!!CharacterSet methodsFor: 'copying' stamp: 'nice 11/20/2007 00:40'!postCopy	map := map copy! !!CharacterSet reorganize!('collection ops' add: do: includes: remove: size)('comparison' = hash species)('conversion' byteComplement complement)('copying' postCopy)('private' byteArrayMap initialize wideCharacterMap)('testing' hasWideCharacters)!